snippet.title: Best VGM 1772 - Pikmin 3 - Plasm Wraith (Final Boss)
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Wii U
Pikmin 3 (2013)
Plasm Wraith (Final Boss)
Asuka Hayazaki, Atsuko Asahi & Hajime Wakai
